title: The Nom Nom Show
description: Things go awry while Nom Nom shoots his first television show. The Bears offer to help and appear on the show.

title: Shmorby
description: The Bears get a Shmorby home assistant device and become lazy couch potatoes.

title: Bearz II Men
description: The Baby Bears help a teenager accomplish his dream of being a famous singer.

title: Coffee Cave
description: After finding out Ice Bear is a master barista, the Bears turn their cave into a popular coffee shop. But it all goes awry when Ice Bear gets too into coffee and goes berserk.

title: Beehive
description: The Bears allow bees to live in the cave to make honey. But soon the Bears, entranced by the honey, become the bees' mindless servants.

title: Fashion Bears
description: In order to abide by the clothing policy of their favorite Boba shop, the Bears get some new outfits. But with new looks come new lives including office work, fashion modeling and even falling in love!

title: Private Lake
description: When the local lake is overcrowded with tourists, the Bears have fun at Charlie's private lake.

title: Lunch with Tabes
description: When Tabes's lunch gets stolen, Tabes launches a full investigation to find the culprit.

title: Charlie Ball
description: After Panda gets injured on the basketball court, the Bears invite Charlie to be on their basketball team. But when Charlie gets too good, he starts to ruin all the fun of the game.

title: Tunnels
description: The Bears discover a network of tunnels underneath the cave. Are they prepared to discover where they lead to and who dug them?

title: Sandcastle
description: The Baby Bears build a giant sandcastle. But when some kids declare war on the Bears, they must fight to defend their new home.

title: Summer Love
description: Panda goes on a mission to return a lost phone to the girl of his dreams.

title: Planet Bears
description: A nature documentary follows the Bears through their normal routine, which includes a trip to the grocery store.

title: Dance Lessons
description: Panda volunteers to be Lucy's partner for a dance contest. But Panda doesn't have the heart to tell Lucy that she's a terrible dancer.

title: Ralph
description: Charlie meets a creature just like him named Ralph. Charlie loves having a new friend, but the Bears think Ralph is bad news.

title: Panda's Art
description: Panda paints a portrait of Charlie and it's a hit with his art class. But after an art dealer offers to buy the painting, Panda has to get it back from Charlie.

title: Lazer Royale
description: The Baby Bears sign up for a game of laser tag, hoping to win some ice cream. But, the round of laser tag turns out to be less of a game and more like a war zone.

title: The Demon
description: Chloe and Ice Bear accidentally lose Chloe's prized hoodie to the ferocious dog next store. They go on a mission to get it back.

title: Fire!
description: Grizz's quick thinking prevents a potential wild fire, but the praise he receives from doing so quickly goes to his head.

title: Our Stuff
description: After the bears play a little pickup basketball (they're very bad), they go back to grab their stuff by the side of the court only to find it's been stolen!  The Bears race across town trying to track down their stuff and end up cracking a giant case in the process.

title: Ice Cave
description: Ralph takes over the cave and turns it into a snowy fortress where he reigns as king over the Bears and Charlie.

title: Panda 2
description: Baby Panda happily lives in a closed off environment for study. But when he's given a new friend, Panda 2, his worldview is shaken, which sets him off on a great adventure.

title: Hot Sauce
description: A quest for their favorite hot sauce causes the Bears to get involved with a sting operation.

title: Dog Hotel
description: With no place to stay while their cave gets fumigated, the Bears book a night at a hotel for dogs.

title: Lord of the Poppies
description: Grizz and the Poppy Rangers go camping on an island, but they soon find themselves deserted.

title: The Perfect Tree
description: Chloe and Ice Bear drive up north to find the perfect Christmas tree. Meanwhile, Grizz and Panda are in charge of decorating Chloe's house.

title: The Fair
description: The Baby Bears make a deal with a carnival worker to be prizes for a game of ball toss.

title: Spa Day
description: The Bears have a relaxing day at the spa. Grizz tries to get everything the spa has to offer. Panda gets trapped in the steam room with an old man. And Ice Bear plays ping pong.

title: Bear Cleanse
description: A doctor tells the Bears to go on a cleanse to improve their health. But when Grizz realizes he can only eat what grizzly bears eat, he starts to lose his mind.

title: Go Fish
description: While on a fishing trip, the Bears get attacked by a giant legendary fish.

title: Cousin Jon
description: When the Bears attend Chloe's family reunion, they fall victim to the mischievous pranks of Chloe's cousin, Jon.

title: Ranger Norm
description: When Tabes leaves for a conference, the Bears have to deal with her substitute, Ranger Norm.

title: Charlie's Halloween Thing 2
description: Charlie tells some scary stories featuring the Bears and their friends.

title: Road Trip
description: Chloe and the Bears take a road trip to see a meteor shower. Ice Bear, the only one licensed to drive, is put in charge, which becomes harder than he thought.
The Baby Bears' dreams come true when they find a 100 dollar bill. But when they can't bear to spend it, they realize it's difficult to let go.

title: Crowbar Jones
description: Grizz screens an epic amateur movie he just made for a focus group. But when he notices people are leaving he must figure out ways to keep the audience engaged.

title: Googs
description: The Bears win a tour of the infamous Googs corporate headquarters.

title: El Oso
description: In a flashback to long ago, Charlie has an adventure in the Mexican desert.

title: Imaginary Friend
description: The Baby Bears invent an imaginary friend, but the trouble he causes is all too real.

title: Viral Video
description: The Bears think they have what it takes to make and star in a viral video, but when Nom-Nom decides that they don't, Grizz breaks into the koala's limo in an effort to change his mind.

title: Nom Nom
description: When Nom Nom shows up on the Bears' doorstep, disheveled and deposed from his spot as cutest internet star ever after a recent meltdown, he enlists the Bears to help him regain his title.

title: Braces
description: When the Bears go to the dentist, Panda gets braces. But, Panda finds out his braces grant him super abilities and the power goes to his head.

title: Tubin'
description: In search of some adventure, the Bears ride a tube down a dangerous river.

title: Adopted
description: The Baby Bears get adopted by an eccentric millionaire and get to live in his mansion.

title: I, Butler
description: The Bears use a robot bear to help around the house. But things get tricky when they lose control of the robot.

title: Charlie's Halloween Thing
description: Charlie hosts an evening of spooky stories starring the Bears.

title: Professor Lampwick
description: Chloe's professor is too mean to give her any face time to talk over her poor grade. The Bears take things into their own hands to help, causing big trouble for Chloe.

title: Teacher's Pet
description: The Baby Bears escape their hectic lives by attending school.

title: Best Bears
description: The Bears must complete their Best-Man duties on the day of Darrell's wedding.

title: Ramen
description: The Baby Bears help a struggling ramen chef perfect her ramen and save her shop.

title: Subway
description: The Bears are stranded on a subway platform after missing their train. But while waiting, the Bears are challenged with recovering some lost items.

title: Paperboyz
description: The Baby Bears get jobs as paper boys.

title: Jean Jacket
description: The Bears find a bedazzled jean jacket in a dumpster. It's just about the coolest thing they've ever seen and seems to make the wearer of the jacket extremely lucky. But after the Bears fight over who gets control of the jacket, they have to consider that their denim blessing has become a curse.

title: Pizza Band
description: The Bears get pizza at Papa Bear's Pizza Cave and wind up replacing the place's animatronic band. They're such a hit that they go on tour!

title: The Mall
description: The Bears go the mall and encounter their human counterparts.

title: Rescue Ranger
description: Tabes helps the Bears rescue Charlie after he gets captured by a villainous game hunter.

title: The Kitty
description: After a mishap in the forest, the Bears lose their own home to dangerous animals.

title: Bunnies
description: The Baby Bears meet a group of helpless bunnies. When they find out the bunnies live in fear of vicious crows, the Bears decide to become heroes and help out.

title: The Limo
description: To help distract Panda from his girl problems, Grizz and Ice Bear treat him to a ride in a limo.

title: More Everyone's Tube
description: Through another video browsing session online, we get more videos uploaded by the Bears and their friends.

title: Lil' Squid
description: The Baby Bears build a submarine and explore the depths of an aquarium so they can bring a lost squid to its family.

title: Anger Management
description: In order to appear on a successful kids show, Nom Nom must successfully complete anger management, with Grizz as his partner.

title: Lucy's Brother
description: To impress Lucy Panda offers to babysit her brother, Clifford. But Clifford turns out to be too high maintenance for Panda to handle.

title: Neighbors
description: Some new neighbors set up camp next to the Bears' cave. Panda and Ice love it, but Grizz thinks they're up to no good.

title: Ranger Games
description: Grizz helps Ranger Tabes and the Poppy Rangers play a game of kickball against their rivals.

title: Bro Brawl
description: The Bears participate in a brother-themed game show against Panda's ex-BFF, Tom, and his roommates.

title: The Park
description: The Bears spend a day at the park. Grizz works out. Panda attempts to sell his artwork. Ice Bear trains some kids.

title: Christmas Movies
description: On Christmas Eve, the Baby Bears defend a video store from getting robbed.

title: Kyle
description: Nom Nom is reunited with his long lost brother, Kyle.

title: Bros in the City
description: The Bears star in a reality TV show along with Griff, Tom, and Isaac.

title: Icy Nights II
description: Ice Bear goes on a late-night adventure to rescue his friend, Yana, from some familiar foes.

title: Escandalosos
description: The Baby Bears enter a Mexican wrestling tournament.

title: The Gym
description: The Bears go to the gym and get quite the work out.

title: Snake Babies
description: Charlie adopts baby snakes despite the Bears thinking he's not ready for parenthood.

title: Bear Lift
description: To help raise money to save Darrell's store, the Bears use the stack as a taxi through a ride share app.

title: Baby Bears Can't Jump
description: In order to win a pizza, the Baby Bears play basketball against a ragtag gang of kids.

title: Bear Squad
description: Tabes deputizes the Bears so they can go to the city and catch a thief.

title: Mom App
description: Hoping to finally get the mom-experience, the Bears use an app that'll bring a mom right to their door.

title: Citizen Tabes
description: After accidentally wounding an animal, Ranger Tabes quits her job. The Bears do what they can to coax her out of retirement.

title: Poppy Rangers
description: Ranger Tabes leads a troop of young girls into a cave expedition, and brings Grizz as their cave expert.

title: Vacation
description: Nom Nom is ordered by his doctor to take a vacation. But he's paired with an unlikely travel buddy- Grizz.

title: Baby Orphan Ninja Bears
description: The Baby Bears venture into the sewers and meet a ninja-like martial arts master.

title: Pigeons
description: Grizz becomes best buds with a flock of pigeons.

title: Crowbar Jones: Origins
description: Grizz pitches his Crowbar Jones prequel film to Nom Nom, hoping Nom Nom will agree to appear in the movie.

title: I Am Ice Bear
description: After Ice Bear hits his head, Grizz and Panda notice him acting like a different person.

title: Panda's Friend
description: Panda uses an app to find a friend with whom he has more common with. Soon things take a turn for the worse when the new friend gets too possessive.

title: Primal
description: Have the Bears lost their survival instincts by living in the modern world? Grizz wants to know so he purposefully gets the Bears lost in the deep forest.

title: Charlie's Big Foot
description: After Charlie hurts his foot, The Bears have to sneak him into a hospital for medical assistance.

title: Rooms
description: The Bears switch bedrooms for the night and get a glimpse of the living space of one of their brothers. But the deeper they go, hidden secrets are revealed.

title: Losing Ice
description: Feeling unappreciated, Ice Bear leaves his brothers to be the chef of a restaurant. Desperate to fill the void, Grizz and Panda look for Ice Bear's replacement.

title: Money Man
description: The Bears help Chloe present her project for a college science contest. But Chloe's rival makes things difficult.

title: Bubble
description: Panda becomes a germophobe and decides to live the rest of his life in a bubble.

title: Wingmen
description: In order to get some sleep, the Bears help an annoying bird find a new mate.
